org.intermine.webservice.client.core

Interface Request

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiPartRequest, QueryService.QueryRequest, RequestImpl, TemplateService.TemplateRequest

    public interface Request
    Client request interface. Client creates the request using following methods and sends it to the server.
